        (a) Note the date and time.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-14335 mb-requirement-id-14337">
        (b) Note the location and habitat.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-14335 mb-requirement-id-14338">
        (c) Describe the bird's main feeding habitat and list two types of food
